{
  "texts": [
    "Another noteworthy challenge in building an automated solution for generating TSs from these real requirements is that the requirements are intricately entwined with domain-specific knowledge, often beyond the information readily available in public sources.",
    "For instance, while some domain information related to the postage and delivery is publicly available, most internal processes at Austrian Post or LIEF POST remain proprietary.",
    "This also means that the pre-trained LLMs have a limited understanding of these processes.",
    "For example, in the example TS in Fig. 1, keywords and processes are specific to LIEF POST.",
    "VB mode (short for Vorbereitung in German), in step 1 of the TS, refers to the preparation phase in LIEF POST."
  ]
}